Instructions:

git clone http://github.com/dbolson/dotvim.git ~/.vim
ln -s ~/.vim/vimrc ~/.vimrc
ln -s ~/.vim/gvimrc ~/.gvimrc
cd ~/.vim
git submodule init
git submodule update

To install JSHint:
  brew install node
  curl https://npmjs.org/install.sh | sh
  npm install -g jshint

To install ctags:
  download from http://sourceforge.net/projects/ctags/files/ctags/5.8/ctags-5.8.tar.gz/download?use_mirror=softlayer
  tar xzvf ctags-5.8.tar.gz
  cd ctags-5.8
  ./configure
  make
  sudo make install

  if there are any problems, read this: http://runtime-era.blogspot.com/2012/05/exuberant-ctags-in-osx-107.html
